{title: Home Wasn't Built In A Day}
{artist: Cal Smith}
{composer: Written by Larry Kingston}

[G]I close the [D7]office at [G]five
And I hurry [D7]home to my [G]wife
[C]While some [D7]men search and [G]roam
I'm satis[D7]fied here at [G]home
